query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Flemish','Italian','Estonian','Latvian','Swedish','Hindi','Danish','Mongolian','Faroese','Kazakh') AND cct1.kind not in ('cast','complete+verified') AND (k.keyword like '%assassin%' OR k.keyword like '%chase%') AND mi_idx.info > '2.0' AND cct2.kind not in ('complete+verified','crew','complete') AND (n.name like '%k%' OR n.name like '%g%' OR n.name like '%x%' OR n.name like '%O%' OR n.name like '%B%') AND n.gender in ('m') AND it2.info in ('crazy credits','screenplay-teleplay','LD disc size','LD analog right','LD color rendition','rating','LD disc format','votes distribution','adaption','LD frequency response','LD master format','LD picture format','book','birth notes','LD length','admissions','LD additional information','top 250 rank','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','weekend gross','LD audio noise') AND it1.info in ('genres','salary history','other works','admissions','interviews','portrayed in','bottom 10 rank','printed media reviews','LD contrast','gross') AND t.production_year > 1997 AND t.production_year < 2000 AND t.title not like '%girl%' AND t.title not like '%door%' AND t.title not like '%apple%' AND t.title not like '%death%' AND t.title not like '%pen%'
